olor: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Bomb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;a piece of bad code deliberately planted by an insider or supplier of a program which explode when certain conditions of explosion get fulfilled causing the damage immediately&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Worm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;copies itself to another machine on the network&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. Rounding Down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;rounding of small fractions of a denomination and transferring these small fractions into an authorized account. As the amount is small, it rarely gets noticed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. Salami Techniques&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;involves slicing of small amounts of money from a computerized transaction or account&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;7. Trap Doors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Allow insertion of specific logic such as program interrupts that permit a review of data. They also permit insertion of unauthorized logic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;8. Spoofing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt; duplicates the login procedure, captures the users password&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;9. Asynchronous Attacks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Data that is waiting to be transmitted are liable to unauthorized access&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Data Leakage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Subversive Attacks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. Wire-Tapping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 144pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;D. Piggybacking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 180pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;electronically&amp;nbsp; attaching&amp;nbsp; to&amp;nbsp; an&amp;nbsp; authorized telecommunication&amp;nbsp; link&amp;nbsp; that&amp;nbsp; intercepts&amp;nbsp; and&amp;nbsp; alters&amp;nbsp; transmissions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;9. Risk Management Strategies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;process of identifying security risks and determining&amp;nbsp; their&amp;nbsp; magnitude&amp;nbsp; and&amp;nbsp; impact&amp;nbsp; on&amp;nbsp; an&amp;nbsp; organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. risk management strategy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Tolerate/Accept the risk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Terminate/Eliminate the risk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. Transfer/Share the risk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Treat/mitigate the risk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;10. ENTERPRISE RISK MANAGEMENT (ERM)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;process affected by an entitys Board of Directors, management and other personnel, applied in strategy setting and across the enterprise, designed to identify potential events that may affect the entity, and manage risk to be within its risk appetite, to provide reasonable assurance regarding the achievement of entity objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Align risk appetite and strategy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Link growth, risk and return&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. Enhance risk response decisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Minimize operational surprises and losses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. Identify and manage cross-enterprise risks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. Provide integrated responses to multiple risks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;7. Seize opportunities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;8. Rationalize capital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;11. Enterprise Risk Management (ERM) Framework&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. framework&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. identifying potential threats or risks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. determining how big a threat or risk is&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. implementing controls to mitigate the risks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. components&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Internal&amp;nbsp; Environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Objective Setting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. Event&amp;nbsp; Identification&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. Risk Assessment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. Risk&amp;nbsp; Response:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. Control Activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;7. Information and Communication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;8. Monitoring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;12. CONTROLS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;policies, procedures, practices and organization structure that are designed to provide&amp;nbsp; reasonable assurance that business objectives are achieved and undesired events are&amp;nbsp; prevented or detected and corrected.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Types of controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Manual&amp;nbsp; Control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Automated&amp;nbsp; Control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. Semi-Automated&amp;nbsp; Control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Controls for the Purchase to Pay cycle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: none ; display: inline-block ; overflow: hidden ; width: 529px ; height: 342px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/rPQSzgdT_5mWL6zFAZOM5yTqHIqY5Fkj5FxOh01XWPZ0z281dp7wK2YYH_i8CzI3iGqZAOT4HlR62QxEjZjM59GbkNadAhEEGeQbVNGmeca-DZ76qPjP-jTDfEVWvECWHzuu915Q&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px ; margin-top: 0px&quot; width=&quot;529&quot; height=&quot;342&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;13. Importance of IT Controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. enable enterprise to achieve objectives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. help in mitigating risks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. promote reliability and efficiency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;D. adapt to changing risk environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;E. uncover the risk and manage its impact&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;14. Applying IT Controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Information Technology General Controls (ITGC)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Information Security Policy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-d